divs: Sighting Detailsi saw it for the first time while going some winterization,it was very close to ground,huge cube shaped and bulging sides like it was over inflated. Red, Green, Blue, Voilet colored lights tumbling around it in a X-pattern.moved up,down side to side,falling fast and then coming back to it spot?is in the nnWestern sky fade to northwest as the night goes by,but not like the stars move in sky.Each night it apears a little farther away,30 days i have seen it when sky is clear. last week we noticed a secondm one in the sky at the same time.three nights ago we found four of them,west north 20degrees east,and then one in the east by northeast sky.all at different degrees up and across. i cann't find anyone with a camera that takes good night photos,but many people have seen it,and i go to the people and give them my binoculars,and show them where to look,and let them TELL ME what they saw.the Air Force Base has changed it's flight zone for it's cargo jets,(C-17)(C-130'S)(C-5A)AND NO JETS HAVE FLOWN OVER MY HOUSE FOR A MONTH,AND THEY HAVE USED THIS ZONE FOR 40 YEARS THAT I KNOW OF!!! THese are E.T.'s,!!!! Not Earth Made Vehicle's... they were out tonight also........NO SOUND,NO HUMAN LIKE PEOPLE?
